<p class= "section">A Collect for Aid against Perils (Tuesday)</p>
<p class= "default">Lighten our darkness, we beseech you, O Lord; and by your great
mercy defend us from all perils and dangers of this night; for the love
of your only Son, our Savior Jesus Christ. 
<span class= "italic"> Amen.</span></p>